The paper discusses the intersection of AI and accessibility, which is most closely related to the field of AI (cs.AI). However, the paper also discusses the social and ethical implications of AI technologies, which falls under the categories of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), cybernetics (cs.CY), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and computer vision (cs.CV).
